#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.10:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Ānisaṃsavagga"
msgstr "1. Benefits"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Vijjāsutta"
msgstr "10. Inspiring All Around: the Three Knowledges"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.10:1.1"
msgid "“Saddho ca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu hoti, no ca sīlavā."
msgstr "“A mendicant is faithful, but not ethical."

msgctxt "an10.10:1.2"
msgid "Evaṃ so tenaṅgena aparipūro hoti."
msgstr "So they’re incomplete in that respect,"

msgctxt "an10.10:1.3"
msgid "Tena taṃ aṅgaṃ paripūretabbaṃ:"
msgstr "and should fulfill it, thinking:"

msgctxt "an10.10:1.4"
msgid "‘kintāhaṃ saddho ca assaṃ sīlavā cā’ti."
msgstr "‘How can I become faithful and ethical?’"

msgctxt "an10.10:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddho ca hoti, sīlavā ca, evaṃ so tenaṅgena "
"paripūro hoti."
msgstr ""
"When the mendicant is faithful and ethical, they’re complete in that respect."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.10:2.1"
msgid ""
"Saddho ca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu hoti sīlavā ca, no ca bahussuto bahussuto ca, "
msgstr "A mendicant is faithful and ethical, but not learned … "

msgctxt "an10.10:2.2"
msgid "no ca dhammakathiko … pe …"
msgstr "they’re not a Dhamma speaker …"

msgctxt "an10.10:2.3"
msgid "dhammakathiko ca, no ca parisāvacaro parisāvacaro ca, "
msgstr "they don’t frequent assemblies … "

msgctxt "an10.10:2.4"
msgid ""
"no ca visārado parisāya dhammaṃ deseti visārado ca parisāya dhammaṃ deseti, "
msgstr "they don’t teach Dhamma to the assembly with assurance … "

msgctxt "an10.10:2.5"
msgid "no ca vinayadharo vinayadharo ca, "
msgstr "they’re not an expert in the training … "

msgctxt "an10.10:2.6"
msgid ""
"no ca anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi "
"jātiyo … pe … iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati. "
"Anekavihitañca … pe … pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati,"
msgstr "they don’t recollect their many kinds of past lives …"

msgctxt "an10.10:2.7"
msgid ""
"no ca dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena … pe … yathākammūpage "
"satte pajānāti dibbena ca cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena … pe …"
msgstr ""
"they don’t, with clairvoyance that is purified and superhuman, see sentient "
"beings passing away and being reborn …"

msgctxt "an10.10:2.8"
msgid ""
"yathākammūpage satte pajānāti, no ca āsavānaṃ khayā … pe … sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"they don’t realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in "
"this very life, and live having realized it with their own insight due to "
"the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "an10.10:2.9"
msgid "Evaṃ so tenaṅgena aparipūro hoti."
msgstr "So they’re incomplete in that respect,"

msgctxt "an10.10:2.10"
msgid "Tena taṃ aṅgaṃ paripūretabbaṃ:"
msgstr "and should fulfill it, thinking:"

msgctxt "an10.10:2.11"
msgid ""
"‘kintāhaṃ saddho ca assaṃ, sīlavā ca, bahussuto ca, dhammakathiko ca, "
"parisāvacaro ca, visārado ca parisāya dhammaṃ deseyyaṃ, vinayadharo ca, "
"anekavihitañca pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi "
"jātiyo … pe … iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyyaṃ, "
"dibbena ca cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena … pe … yathākammūpage "
"satte pajāneyyaṃ, āsavānañca khayā … pe … sacchikatvā upasampajja "
"vihareyyan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘How can I become faithful, ethical, and educated, a Dhamma speaker, one who "
"frequents assemblies, one who teaches Dhamma to the assembly with assurance, "
"an expert in the training, one who recollects their many kinds of past "
"lives, one who with clairvoyance that surpasses the human sees sentient "
"beings passing away and being reborn, and one who lives having realized the "
"ending of defilements?’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.10:3.1"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddho ca hoti, sīlavā ca, bahussuto ca, "
"dhammakathiko ca, parisāvacaro ca, visārado ca parisāya dhammaṃ deseti, "
"vinayadharo ca, anekavihitañca pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, seyyathidaṃ—ekampi "
"jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo … pe … iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ "
"anussarati, dibbena ca cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena … pe … "
"yathākammūpage satte pajānāti, āsavānañca khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ "
"paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"When they are faithful, ethical, and educated, a Dhamma speaker, one who "
"frequents assemblies, one who teaches Dhamma to the assembly with assurance, "
"an expert in the training, one who recollects their many kinds of past "
"lives, one who with clairvoyance that surpasses the human sees sentient "
"beings passing away and being reborn, and one who lives having realized the "
"ending of defilements,"

msgctxt "an10.10:3.2"
msgid "Evaṃ so tenaṅgena paripūro hoti."
msgstr "they’re complete in that respect."

msgctxt "an10.10:3.3"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu samantapāsādiko ca "
"hoti sabbākāraparipūro cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant who has these ten qualities is inspiring all around, and is "
"complete in every aspect.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.10:3.4"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.10:3.5"
msgid "Ānisaṃsavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.10:4.1"
msgid "Kimatthiyaṃ cetanā ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.10:4.2"
msgid "tayo upanisāpi ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.10:4.3"
msgid "Samādhi sāriputto ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.10:4.4"
msgid "jhānaṃ santena vijjayāti."
msgstr ""
